Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.49,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.65,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:53.40,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.21,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.35,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:22.70,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:27.43,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.43,0:01:34.37,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Brother... I am at Saint-Juste-sama's funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,35. Beach of Dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:03:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,On her final day, the day she passed away,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...Saint-Juste-sama sent roses to Fukiko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The day was also unusual in that she'd cleaned her apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...and arranged to return a book to Kaoru-no-Kimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For me... the special day was the one just before,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...when she promised to take me to see the sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She was enveloping us, all of us, with her happiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not believe it was destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it's as if she were passing on her happiness to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...knowing she must soon depart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,After crying so much, my tears still will not stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko, it is time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Brother, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you leave Rei and I alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to say a final farewell, just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but we must take the coffin out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... just five, no, ten minutes more. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we wait longer, I'm afraid the traffic will be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only ten more minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She only lived for 17 years. This is her last ten minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is i impossible to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what the reason is, surely you can wait ten minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei, were you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,During your entire funeral, I did not let one tear escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I never allowed my emotions out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I remained calm and dignified as I accepted the many condolences.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was the proud Fukiko that you have always loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...because you are the only one who can see my tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My tears... my tears are for you only.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei... Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei, I loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I did love you so!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I must say good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved! I was having a terrible dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A very, very scary dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:09:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And where shall it go, this body of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,At one with the wind, wherever it may lead, like a lone sea gull.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Please take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I will fly. Higher... and higher...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...and higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you? It doesn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama I won't stay forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But just a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stay here in this dream just a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside your dream... deep within your dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Being unable to sleep, I went for a walk,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...and before I knew it I was at Saint-Juste-sama's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What if... what if my emotions lead me to her room for a reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There was definitely a flicker of light coming from that room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For a moment I thought you were her, coming back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was merely dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream that her death was just a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I was feeling so grateful that it was only a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I awoke, and realized I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It all must have seemed very peculiar to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The relationship between Rei and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But I did love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to be the only one she admired; if not, I would become anxious...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...terribly anxious...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,With those words, Miya-sama became silent,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the two of us quietly stood there, staring out of the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the window, we could see a canal and the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... yes! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the landscape Saint-Juste-sama looked over every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Miya-sama and I are looking out in place of Saint-Juste-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama, can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It is almost dawn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It begins without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A day is about to start without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is something that you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, my father and brother will come to clean out this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Before they do... perhaps you would like to choose a memento of Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Rei would be glad for you to have something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She liked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma cherie la pupe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You look just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. That will be fine, Nanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know this doll is one I gave to Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I gave it to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to live with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...but keep this near you, and think of me always.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't remember it before, but now I remember clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of that beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama so this is where you've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san, please come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We will take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.83,0:16:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something I swore I'd never reveal to anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:17:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But perhaps I could... ...yes, I do want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, Rei and I are not stepsisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We share both parents, and are full sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman I'd thought was my mother, on her deathbed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...finally told me the truth before she passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the truth was too terrible to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The father in whom I'd trusted had another woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was not a true Ichinomiya, I was her child instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I had a little sister too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So I felt great hatred for Rei or at least, I tried to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't hate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she is my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My only sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't talk to Rei about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew if I told her, she would suffer more than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...at least, I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe I should have told her anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps then I could have loved her in a different way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama had known!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I cried out silently within...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't speak it aloud. I couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:19:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this happen, Dear Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama and Saint-Juste-sama were unaware that the other one knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Each protecting the other from the sad truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I see the strong bond of love between the sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Love, strong beyond my comprehension... a bond of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, the two sisters entrusted me with this secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I will guard this secret forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I will keep it in my heart, secured by a lock marked "forever".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sad, isn't it, how you and I ended up being such wonderful sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sad that we have different mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If we act now, we can stop time at this moment of beautiful sisterhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...nothing will ever take it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise sadness will overtake us, and it will be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss? Are you traveling alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm with my younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If she is your sister, she must be very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We both take after our mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you traveling far?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My journey is at an end...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.86,0:22:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.04,0:22:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It is all over now, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.12,0:22:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We will now discuss the petition submitted by the students,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.12,0:22:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...regarding the abolition of the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.32,0:22:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.05,0:23:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinomiya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.29,0:23:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that you had to convene a meeting on the subject,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.96,0:23:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...but the discussion is not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.63,0:23:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As the president of the Sorority, and as its last member,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.59,0:23:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...I voluntarily request the dissolution of the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sorority has been officially abolished.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,For certain, something has ended, and something has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am left with one fact only... that Saint-Juste-sama has passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.97,0:24:14.18,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:19.64,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:25.23,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.23,0:24:30.69,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.44,0:24:36.99,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.99,0:24:42.46,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.46,0:24:45.21,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.21,0:24:48.00,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.00,0:24:50.42,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.42,0:24:55.68,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
